<p><b>Is Fallen in Love part of the Fallen series?</b> Fallen In Love is a novel written by Lauren Kate and was published on January 24, 2012. This book is a young adult fiction novel based on the characters from that author's most notable series, Fallen.</p>
<p><b>Is Fallen series based on a book?</b> Fallen is an upcoming English-language romantic fantasy television series created by Claudia Bluemhuber, based on the 2009 novel by Lauren Kate.</p>
